    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/44c6f2feb1b1ee48276bd0a9eccd3f39.avif?t=1729672784\" width=500 height=87 /></span><br><br>Afterlife VR是一款沉浸式恐怖游戏, 能够为你带来真正的恐怖感觉.<br><br>在这款游戏中玩家将扮演亚当·伯恩哈德, 一名正在例行夜间巡逻的年轻新秀警官. 没人能想到一个电话将永远改变他生活.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/e5d1ff26ebb89bd25fe9bebddab582a2.poster.avif?t=1729672784\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/e5d1ff26ebb89bd25fe9bebddab582a2.webm?t=1729672784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/e5d1ff26ebb89bd25fe9bebddab582a2.mp4?t=1729672784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>亚当的妹妹艾莉森最近被送往一家有名的精神病院. 那里究竟隐藏着什么? 失踪的患者和医院工作人员与关于蓝色孩子现象开创性研究之间是否有任何联系?<br><br>揭开隐藏在黑玫瑰精神病院墙壁背后的秘密, 那里的大多数患者都对自己和其他人构成了威胁. 那一双双纯碎而疯狂的眼睛, 似乎正发掘着这个地方与其历史之间的某种内在联系.<br><br>你敢一探究竟吗?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/beb00f478f0a0f65cae14a4d0a151701.poster.avif?t=1729672784\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/beb00f478f0a0f65cae14a4d0a151701.webm?t=1729672784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/beb00f478f0a0f65cae14a4d0a151701.mp4?t=1729672784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- 专门为VR打造的沉浸式第一人称恐怖游戏<br>- 令人毛骨悚然的剧情, 让你不禁质疑自己的感官<br>- 创新的解谜设计, 需要利用运动控制器和主角的心灵感应能力<br>- 愉快但又可怕的遭遇 - 用你的枪支和/或你的心灵感应能力与敌人战斗<br>- 探索神秘的黑玫瑰医院, 沉浸在其离奇的故事之中<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/de1a11974fdaa2d01f2de84827e215c2.poster.avif?t=1729672784\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/de1a11974fdaa2d01f2de84827e215c2.webm?t=1729672784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1528020/extras/de1a11974fdaa2d01f2de84827e215c2.mp4?t=1729672784\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
